title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 11/17/2018
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 11/17/2018
description:
Coming off a rough week Colin looks to rebound and gives his Blazing 5 picks to RJ Bell of pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which ones the wise guys in Vegas agree and disagree with. Plus, Colin reveals two bonus picks that were not included in his Blazing 5.
